      <title>uv workspace: effective management of Python apps</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/drafts/uv-packages/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>tabularasa8931@gmail.com (Han)</author>
